1) Install VirtualBox (v4.2.6)
2) Install Ruby 1.9.3-head using RVM (ruby-1.9.3-p385)
3) rvm use 1.9.3-head
4) gem install vagrant
5) Download the ssn_development vagrant box from Google Drive
6) vagrant box add ssn_development [path to ssn_development.box]
7) cd [wherever you put the git repository]/SSN/social-network-engine
8) vagrant up

From there you can use any of the vagrant commands.  See http://www.vagrantup.com/ for more details
